, but because they offer an illuminating, instructive glimpse into the machinations of an economist who wasn’t motivated by publications. Here, and throughout his works, an inquisitive spirit remains remarkable and forever resonant.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aEconomics. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / General.2bisacsh1 aElias, Julio J., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGlaeser, Edward L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlaeser, Edward, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMulligan, Casey B., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMurphy, Kevin M., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2023 Englishz978311131907008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2023z9783111318134oZDB-23-DBV08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311079732940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226827216423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780226827216/original  a978-3-11-079732-9  University of Chicago Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-131907-0  EBOOK PACKAGE Business and Economics 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DBVb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023